      "strokeColor": "#51cf66",
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "THE RAIN SEAM\nthe forward pass is the\narchitectural seam \u2014 the rain\nshader is just a different\npipeline bound in that pass.\nBuild the pass once (Phase 5),\nplug rain in later (Phase 6).",
      "originalText": "THE RAIN SEAM\nthe forward pass is the\narchitectural seam \u2014 the rain\nshader is just a different\npipeline bound in that pass.\nBuild the pass once (Phase 5),\nplug rain in later (Phase 6).",
