    {
      "id": "i4_plan_t",
      "index": "b1P",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "groupIds": [],
      "angle": 0,
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "seed": 250,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 7150,
      "updated": 1781400000000,
      "boundElements": [],
      "type": "text",
      "x": 84,
      "y": 1192,
      "width": 546.0,
      "height": 195.0,
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "strokeColor": "#51cf66",
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "IMPLEMENTED in load_car() \u2014 node-walk loader:\nwalk glTF nodes -> bake inverse(W_RootNode) * W_node into vertices\n(normals via inverse-transpose, tangents via mat3) \u2014 1665/1667 mesh\nnodes have non-identity transforms; this is what put the steering\nwheel + interior in place. RootNode-rel space = meters, Y-up, nose +Z\n-> skip alphaMode==BLEND prims (3 glass; opaque G-buffer would wall\n   off the cockpit \u2014 forward pass lands in Phase 5)\n-> rotate +90 about Y: (x,y,z)->(z,y,-x), nose +Z -> +X\n-> ground: shift min.y -> 0 (now ~0: baked space sits on y=0)\n-> bbox log gate: 4.57 x 1.29 x 2.03 m (real 911 height)\nSTILL PLANNED (Phase 4): articulated pivots (config-named) for\nsteering-wheel rotation \u00b7 glass FLAGS instead of skipping",
      "originalText": "IMPLEMENTED in load_car() \u2014 node-walk loader:\nwalk glTF nodes -> bake inverse(W_RootNode) * W_node into vertices\n(normals via inverse-transpose, tangents via mat3) \u2014 1665/1667 mesh\nnodes have non-identity transforms; this is what put the steering\nwheel + interior in place. RootNode-rel space = meters, Y-up, nose +Z\n-> skip alphaMode==BLEND prims (3 glass; opaque G-buffer would wall\n   off the cockpit \u2014 forward pass lands in Phase 5)\n-> rotate +90 about Y: (x,y,z)->(z,y,-x), nose +Z -> +X\n-> ground: shift min.y -> 0 (now ~0: baked space sits on y=0)\n-> bbox log gate: 4.57 x 1.29 x 2.03 m (real 911 height)\nSTILL PLANNED (Phase 4): articulated pivots (config-named) for\nsteering-wheel rotation \u00b7 glass FLAGS instead of skipping",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "containerId": null,
      "autoResize": true
    },
