    {
      "id": "i5_eq_t",
      "index": "b1o",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "groupIds": [],
      "angle": 0,
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "seed": 275,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 7175,
      "updated": 1781400000000,
      "boundElements": [],
      "type": "text",
      "x": 964,
      "y": 1092,
      "width": 331.2,
      "height": 150.0,
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "strokeColor": "#f1f3f5",
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "DRIVING MODEL (all SI, x WORLD_SCALE=1000)\nconvention: forward = R_y(yaw)*(+X) = (cos, 0, -sin)\n  loader puts mesh nose at +X -> body == velocity\n  yaw +90 faces -Z (down road) \u00b7 +yaw turns LEFT\nbicycle model:  omega = v * tan(delta) / L\n  yaw -= omega*dt   (positive steer = right)\nsteering fade:  d_eff = d_max / (1 + K*v^2)\n0-60 mph in 4.4 s  (a=6.43, vmax=69.44 m/s)\ncruise decel: c_rr*g + c_d*v^2 (rolling+drag)\nA/D steer at 90 deg/s, spring-return 120 deg/s",
      "originalText": "DRIVING MODEL (all SI, x WORLD_SCALE=1000)\nconvention: forward = R_y(yaw)*(+X) = (cos, 0, -sin)\n  loader puts mesh nose at +X -> body == velocity\n  yaw +90 faces -Z (down road) \u00b7 +yaw turns LEFT\nbicycle model:  omega = v * tan(delta) / L\n  yaw -= omega*dt   (positive steer = right)\nsteering fade:  d_eff = d_max / (1 + K*v^2)\n0-60 mph in 4.4 s  (a=6.43, vmax=69.44 m/s)\ncruise decel: c_rr*g + c_d*v^2 (rolling+drag)\nA/D steer at 90 deg/s, spring-return 120 deg/s",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "containerId": null,
      "autoResize": true
    },
