      "strokeColor": "#f1f3f5",
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "ARTICULATED PARTS (no scene graph)\npart = {submesh range, pivot P, axis, angle}\nmodel = M_car * T(P) * R(axis,th) * T(-P)\nnow:  SteeringWheel_Pivot (th = -delta*ratio)\ndeferred: wheel spin \u2014 GLB has no wheel\npivots -> re-export from porsche.blend",
      "originalText": "ARTICULATED PARTS (no scene graph)\npart = {submesh range, pivot P, axis, angle}\nmodel = M_car * T(P) * R(axis,th) * T(-P)\nnow:  SteeringWheel_Pivot (th = -delta*ratio)\ndeferred: wheel spin \u2014 GLB has no wheel\npivots -> re-export from porsche.blend",
