      "text": "COCKPIT MATH (no scene graph needed) \u2014 IMPLEMENTED (simple version)\neye   = M_car x kSeatEye          (-0.32, 1.05, -0.34) m, normalized\n                                  mesh space; scale 1000 = m -> WU\n                                  (wheel center: 0.18, 0.76, -0.34)\nyaw   = -car_heading + look_yaw   (cam fwd = (cos,.,sin);\n                                   car fwd = (cos,0,-sin))\nlook  clamped: yaw +-150 deg, pitch +-60 deg \u00b7 reset on mode toggle\nC key toggles Cockpit <-> FreeFly (edge-detected) \u2014 App.cpp\nPLANNED (CameraController): FOV-speed lerp, head bob, per-mode near",
      "originalText": "COCKPIT MATH (no scene graph needed) \u2014 IMPLEMENTED (simple version)\neye   = M_car x kSeatEye          (-0.32, 1.05, -0.34) m, normalized\n                                  mesh space; scale 1000 = m -> WU\n                                  (wheel center: 0.18, 0.76, -0.34)\nyaw   = -car_heading + look_yaw   (cam fwd = (cos,.,sin);\n                                   car fwd = (cos,0,-sin))\nlook  clamped: yaw +-150 deg, pitch +-60 deg \u00b7 reset on mode toggle\nC key toggles Cockpit <-> FreeFly (edge-detected) \u2014 App.cpp\nPLANNED (CameraController): FOV-speed lerp, head bob, per-mode near",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
