      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "strokeColor": "#f1f3f5",
      "roundness": null,
      "text": "porsche.glb: 3341 nodes \u00b7 13.9 MB \u00b7 embedded PBR textures\nnode chain: Sketchfab(S=1000, R=-90X) -> fbx(S=0.01, R=+90X)\n            -> RootNode   ==> nets ~10x scale, rotations cancel\nloader normalizes: nose +Z -> +X \u00b7 grounded min.y -0.362 -> 0\nbbox 4.57 x 1.66 x 2.03 m (logged at load as the size gate)\nwheels: all four FLATTENED under one node (1138 children)\n        -> no pivots -> wheel spin deferred\nSteeringWheel_Pivot: clean, animatable today\nspawn today: (6501, 0, -20000) \u00b7 yaw +90 \u00b7 entity scale 1000",
      "originalText": "porsche.glb: 3341 nodes \u00b7 13.9 MB \u00b7 embedded PBR textures\nnode chain: Sketchfab(S=1000, R=-90X) -> fbx(S=0.01, R=+90X)\n            -> RootNode   ==> nets ~10x scale, rotations cancel\nloader normalizes: nose +Z -> +X \u00b7 grounded min.y -0.362 -> 0\nbbox 4.57 x 1.66 x 2.03 m (logged at load as the size gate)\nwheels: all four FLATTENED under one node (1138 children)\n        -> no pivots -> wheel spin deferred\nSteeringWheel_Pivot: clean, animatable today\nspawn today: (6501, 0, -20000) \u00b7 yaw +90 \u00b7 entity scale 1000",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "containerId": null,
      "autoResize": true
